The filename in Payabli. Filename is `zipName` in the response to a request to `/api/Invoice/{idInvoice}`. Here, the filename is `0_Bill.pdf``. 
```
  "DocumentsRef": {
    "zipfile": "inva_269.zip",
    "filelist": [
      {
        "originalName": "Bill.pdf",
        "zipName": "0_Bill.pdf",
        "descriptor": null
      }
    ]
  }
  ```

